      • markdown

        public static Message.Text markdown(java.lang.String markdown,
                                    java.lang.String html,
                                    java.lang.String plain)
        Make a Text object for the markdown.
        参数:
        markdown - the text with the markdown markup.
        html - the html text for how to render the markdown.
        plain - the alternate plain text for cases that do not support markdown and html markup.
